      <title>明链网络VPN配置手册</title>
      <link href="/2018/07/04/mchain-network/"/>
      <url>/2018/07/04/mchain-network/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、概述"><a href="#一、概述" class="headerlink" title="一、概述"></a>一、概述</h2><p>现在北京和深圳两地有办公室，都可以通过VPN接入网络。</p><p>北京VPN接入服务器是固定IP<strong>61.149.7.240</strong></p><p>深圳VPN接入服务器为动态域名<strong>sino-cloud.ticp.io</strong></p><h2 id="二、创建VPN"><a href="#二、创建VPN" class="headerlink" title="二、创建VPN"></a>二、创建VPN</h2><h3 id="1、Mac"><a href="#1、Mac" class="headerlink" title="1、Mac"></a>1、Mac</h3><p>打开系统偏好设置，选择网络</p><p><img src="/images/00-System.png" alt="系统偏好设置"></p><p>点击左下角的“+”号，创建一个新的服务</p><p><img src="/images/01-MacNewVPN.png" alt="网络"></p><p>接口选择<strong>VPN</strong>，VPN类型选择<strong>L2TP/IPSec</strong>，服务名称随意输入，点击“创建”按钮</p><p><img src="/images/02-MacSetupVPN.png" alt="新服务"></p><p>配置选择<strong>默认</strong>，北京服务器地址输入<strong>61.149.7.240</strong>，深圳服务器地址输入<strong>sino-cloud.ticp.io</strong>，帐户名称输入<strong>mchainvpn</strong></p><p><img src="/images/03-MacSetupVPN.png" alt="配置"></p><p>点击“鉴定设置”按钮，在用户鉴定和机器鉴定处输入密码（另行告知），点击“好”按钮</p><p><img src="/images/04-MacSetupVPN.png" alt="鉴定设置"></p><p>点击“应用”按钮保存设置</p><p><img src="/images/05-MacSetupVPN.png" alt="应用"></p><p>点击“连接”按钮进行测试</p><p>如果没有意外，应该显示已连接，北京会分配一个<strong>192.168.138</strong>网段的IP地址，深圳会分配一个<strong>192.168.139</strong>网段的IP地址</p><p><img src="/images/06-MacConnectVPN.png" alt="连接"></p><p>在终端里面执行命令<strong>ping 192.168.138.1</strong>，检测是否可以连通网关</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ping 192.168.138.1</span><br><span class="line">PING 192.168.138.1 (192.168.138.1): 56 data bytes</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 192.168.138.1: icmp_seq=0 ttl=64 time=54.491 ms</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 192.168.138.1: icmp_seq=1 ttl=64 time=28.730 ms</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 192.168.138.1: icmp_seq=2 ttl=64 time=31.256 ms</span><br><span class="line">^C</span><br><span class="line">--- 192.168.138.1 ping statistics ---</span><br><span class="line">3 packets transmitted, 3 packets received, 0.0% packet loss</span><br><span class="line">round-trip min/avg/max/stddev = 28.730/38.159/54.491/11.594 ms</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、Windows-10"><a href="#2、Windows-10" class="headerlink" title="2、Windows 10"></a>2、Windows 10</h3><p>待补充</p><h2 id="三、手工添加路由"><a href="#三、手工添加路由" class="headerlink" title="三、手工添加路由"></a>三、手工添加路由</h2><p>通过VPN连接到北京或者深圳后，默认只能访问当地的网络资源，如果需要访问其他地方的网络，还需要手工添加路由信息。</p><p>注：北京网络为192.168.138.0/24，深圳网络为192.168.139.0/24，本例连接到深圳VPN，添加路由访问北京网络</p><h2 id="1、Mac-1"><a href="#1、Mac-1" class="headerlink" title="1、Mac"></a>1、Mac</h2><p>连接到深圳的VPN服务器，应该获取到<strong>192.168.139</strong>网段的IP地址</p><p><img src="/images/08-MacRoute.png" alt="已连接"></p><p>打开终端，执行<strong>ping 192.168.139.1</strong>，应该可以连通</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ping 192.168.139.1</span><br><span class="line">PING 192.168.139.1 (192.168.139.1): 56 data bytes</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 192.168.139.1: icmp_seq=0 ttl=64 time=43.084 ms</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 192.168.139.1: icmp_seq=1 ttl=64 time=33.398 ms</span><br><span class="line">--- 192.168.139.1 ping statistics ---</span><br><span class="line">3 packets transmitted, 2 packets received, 33.3% packet loss</span><br><span class="line">round-trip min/avg/max/stddev = 33.398/38.241/43.084/4.843 ms</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开终端，执行<strong>ping 192.168.138.1</strong>，应该无法连通</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ping 192.168.138.1</span><br><span class="line">PING 192.168.138.1 (192.168.138.1): 56 data bytes</span><br><span class="line">Request timeout for icmp_seq 0</span><br><span class="line">--- 192.168.138.1 ping statistics ---</span><br><span class="line">2 packets transmitted, 0 packets received, 100.0% packet loss</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开终端，执行命令添加路由信息<strong>sudo route add 192.168.138.0 192.168.139.1</strong>，输入密码，成功</p><p>注：连接到北京VPN，应该执行<strong>sudo route add 192.168.139.0 192.168.138.1</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo route add 192.168.138.0 192.168.139.1</span><br><span class="line">Password:</span><br><span class="line">add net 192.168.138.0: gateway 192.168.139.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开终端，执行<strong>ping 192.168.138.1</strong>，应该可以连通了</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ping 192.168.138.1</span><br><span class="line">PING 192.168.138.1 (192.168.138.1): 56 data bytes</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 192.168.138.1: icmp_seq=0 ttl=63 time=79.593 ms</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 192.168.138.1: icmp_seq=1 ttl=63 time=72.609 ms</span><br><span class="line">64 bytes from 192.168.138.1: icmp_seq=2 ttl=63 time=75.088 ms</span><br><span class="line">--- 192.168.138.1 ping statistics ---</span><br><span class="line">3 packets transmitted, 3 packets received, 0.0% packet loss</span><br><span class="line">round-trip min/avg/max/stddev = 72.609/75.763/79.593/2.891 ms</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注：可以自行搜索将路由加为永久路由</p><h3 id="2、Windows"><a href="#2、Windows" class="headerlink" title="2、Windows"></a>2、Windows</h3><p>待补充</p>]]></content>
      
      
