      <title>Mchain Shenzhen VPN Setup</title>
      <link href="/2018/07/01/Mchain-VPN-Setup/"/>
      <url>/2018/07/01/Mchain-VPN-Setup/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、验证VPN服务器域名"><a href="#一、验证VPN服务器域名" class="headerlink" title="一、验证VPN服务器域名"></a>一、验证VPN服务器域名</h2><p>在终端执行如下命令nslookup sino-cloud.ticp.io，应该可以通过动态域名找到深圳办公室网络的公网IP地址（这个地址经常变化，发生改变后，会通过脚本自动更新，但是会有滞后）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ nslookup sino-cloud.ticp.io</span><br><span class="line">Server:192.168.2.1</span><br><span class="line">Address:192.168.2.1<span class="comment">#53</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Non-authoritative answer:</span><br><span class="line">Name:sino-cloud.ticp.io</span><br><span class="line">Address: 121.34.***.***</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二、在Mac上新建VPN连接"><a href="#二、在Mac上新建VPN连接" class="headerlink" title="二、在Mac上新建VPN连接"></a>二、在Mac上新建VPN连接</h2><p><img src="/images/02-CreateVPN.gif" alt="02-CreateVPN"></p><p>注：操作里面输入的密码另外告知</p><h2 id="三、连接到VPN"><a href="#三、连接到VPN" class="headerlink" title="三、连接到VPN"></a>三、连接到VPN</h2><h3 id="1、点击连接按钮，连接成功后，应该获得一个局域网IP地址（192-168-1-160-179之间）"><a href="#1、点击连接按钮，连接成功后，应该获得一个局域网IP地址（192-168-1-160-179之间）" class="headerlink" title="1、点击连接按钮，连接成功后，应该获得一个局域网IP地址（192.168.1.160-179之间）"></a>1、点击连接按钮，连接成功后，应该获得一个局域网IP地址（192.168.1.160-179之间）</h3><p><img src="/images/03-ConnectVPN.gif" alt="03-ConnectVPN"></p><h3 id="2、用ssh命令连接服务器来检测VPN工作是否正常"><a href="#2、用ssh命令连接服务器来检测VPN工作是否正常" class="headerlink" title="2、用ssh命令连接服务器来检测VPN工作是否正常"></a>2、用ssh命令连接服务器来检测VPN工作是否正常</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ssh x3550m4@192.168.1.120</span><br><span class="line">x3550m4@192.168.1.120<span class="string">'s password: </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Welcome to Ubuntu 16.04.4 LTS (GNU/Linux 4.13.0-45-generic x86_64)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"> * Documentation:  https://help.ubuntu.com</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"> * Management:     https://landscape.canonical.com</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"> * Support:        https://ubuntu.com/advantage</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">0 个可升级软件包。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">0 个安全更新。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">*** 需要重启系统 ***</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Last login: Sun Jul  1 12:13:52 2018 from 192.168.1.160</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">x3550m4@x3550m4-02:~$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
